{"tid":515474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺做人，一定要對自己坦白，對人坦白","createTime":"2017-12-31T12:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T18:54:57.000Z","uid":123335,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4310509190a59de867b5b54648de8dc87d63af","tid":515474,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"收收埋埋，扮無野無事，口不對心，絕對係有害<br />\nEg 冇女，咪坦白認冇女<br />\n冇女又想有女，咪坦白認冇女又想有女<br />\n見到街上有個索女，想扑佢，咪坦白認想扑佢<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁做？<br />\n因為當你向自己誠實，向他人大方坦白時<br />\n你至係活在現實<br />\n活在當下<br />\n而唔係活係幻想，活係ff中，同現實脫鈎<br />\n<br />\n人只有活在現實下<br />\n先會係現實世界中進步<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我做咗25年人最大嘅心得<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新嘅一年新嘅開始<br />\n希望大家都有進步"},{"pid":"e5d20c60a2d1ecd074e9b688b6c9218685163a1c","tid":515474,"uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"我發覺對自己，對人坦白大方<br />\n有時係會俾人笑自己柒 笑自己毒 笑自己on9 <br />\n但正正就係因為俾人笑9自己<br />\n甚至有時連自己都笑9自己果陣<br />\n<br />\n就係呢個moment <br />\n自己就會有motive去正視自己個問題<br />\n慢慢一步步進步<br />\n<br />\n其實真係做人唔好怕柒<br />\n男人老狗怕呢樣 怕果樣<br />\n怕係蝕底咁<br />\n渣架"},{"pid":"ecebbe5e39a91c9614accbdb4c4c7f5658f450f0","tid":515474,"uid":17379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"我都覺，想咪大大方方認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e092c0afaff01b179dfd6d768937ca0d32fee1","tid":515474,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecebbe5e39a91c9614accbdb4c4c7f5658f450f0","tid":515474,"uid":17379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"我都覺，想咪大大方方認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"懶係要面果啲<br />\n怕出羞 怕柒<br />\n最終會發覺，蝕底既係自己"},{"pid":"bd3696ebb6dd1fbfba3505be58a3e91879653977","tid":515474,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"又講得幾啱wor，咁我大方承認覺得好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1e6c3b46ccf9e9fae8f47583dd21bb9f53ac23","tid":515474,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"講大話真係好攰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbc9d5e80ec5ddebba0677995c8291ba5365735","tid":515474,"uid":154031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"對自己誠實真係好緊要。"},{"pid":"ed300a719a112e165d4049512a40fd3665d6b771","tid":515474,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd3696ebb6dd1fbfba3505be58a3e91879653977","tid":515474,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"又講得幾啱wor，咁我大方承認覺得好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:40:08.000Z","msg":"認咪認<br />\n怕咩認？<br />\n<br />\n其實有時你俾人知你寂莫，你自己都認寂莫<br />\n你自己會唔覺唔覺，慢慢正視問題<br />\n然後逐d逐d 改善"},{"pid":"0e6d7821807c959717c7ed1a3a5b162bdaf7a563","tid":515474,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed300a719a112e165d4049512a40fd3665d6b771","tid":515474,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd3696ebb6dd1fbfba3505be58a3e91879653977","tid":515474,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"又講得幾啱wor，咁我大方承認覺得好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:40:08.000Z","msg":"認咪認<br />\n怕咩認？<br />\n<br />\n其實有時你俾人知你寂莫，你自己都認寂莫<br />\n你自己會唔覺唔覺，慢慢正視問題<br />\n然後逐d逐d 改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得寂寞係一個好麻煩的問題，我唔可以單靠自己去解決"},{"pid":"db3f8073432d3a712d8b8cda6e88363683d4fcdf","tid":515474,"uid":163627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"對自己坦白好啦<br />\n對其他人就唔洗啦"},{"pid":"129c6affde4b57ccf26bd8212a5470ccf7e6b66d","tid":5154